## Definition of done

A change is ready to merge when:

- [ ] `make check` (or equivalent) passes locally
- [ ] New behaviour has test coverage
- [ ] Any new architectural decision is recorded in `docs/adr/`
- [ ] `docs/` updated if the change affects documented behaviour
- [ ] CI is green on the PR
